            </section>

            <section class="section">
                <h2>Built for You</h2>
                <p>We know that finding the right association can feel overwhelming. So You is designed with intention:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Clear navigation</strong> — A bottom bar that stays put, so you always know where you are</li>
                    <li><strong>Generous spacing</strong> — Room to breathe between every element</li>
                    <li><strong>Calm aesthetics</strong> — Soft colors, rounded edges, and no visual clutter</li>
                    <li><strong>Neurodivergent-friendly</strong> — Created with ADHD, autism, and sensory sensitivities in mind</li>
                </ul>
